---

<BaseLayout
  title="Geometry Dash Meltdown Unblocked – Play Free Online (New Levels)"
  description="Play Geometry Dash Meltdown Unblocked online for free! A spin-off with new levels, dark music, and unique themes. No download required. Play now!"
  keywords="geometry dash meltdown, geometry dash meltdown online, geometry dash meltdown free, dark platformer game"
  jsonLd={[gameSchema]}
  ogImage="/assets/covers/geometry-dash-meltdown-gameplay-screenshot-dark-neon.png"
>
  <Header />
  
  <main id="main-content">
    <div class="container">
      <Breadcrumbs items={breadcrumbItems} />
      
      <article class="game-page">
        <header class="game-header">
          <div class="game-icon">
            <img src="/assets/icons/geometrydashmeltdown-icon.webp" alt="Geometry Dash Meltdown Icon" width="120" height="120" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <h1>Geometry Dash Meltdown – Play Free Online</h1>
          
          <div class="game-intro">
            <p><strong>Geometry Dash Meltdown</strong> is an exciting spin-off featuring completely new levels, fresh music tracks, and unique dark visual themes. Experience the same addictive rhythm-platformer gameplay with completely new challenges and a darker aesthetic that sets it apart from the original game.</p>
          </div>
          
